  <div class="page">
    <p><b>Tanhai.</b></p>
    <p>
      Yeh sirf akela hona nahi hota,
      balki woh pal hota hai  
      jab dil khud se baat karta hai.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <p>
      Log paas the,
      par baatein door thi.
    </p>
    <p>
      Aur main bheed ke beech  
      khud ko dhoondhta reh gaya.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <p>
      Raat ko khamoshi zyada bolti thi,
    </p>
    <p>
      har yaad ek sawaal ban kar
      saamne aa jaati thi.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <p>
      Kabhi uska naam soch kar
      muskurahat aa jaati,
    </p>
    <p>
      aur agle hi pal  
      aankhen bheeg jaati.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <p>
      Tanhai ne mujhe kamzor nahi banaya,
    </p>
    <p>
      bas thoda gehra kar diya.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <p>
      Ab main kam bolta hoon,
    </p>
    <p>
      par jo mehsoos karta hoon  
      woh zyada sach hota hai.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <p>
      Shayad tanhai bhi ek kitaab hai,
    </p>
    <p>
      jo sirf wohi padh sakta hai  
      jo toota ho.
    </p>
  </div>

